    ''' -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
    ''' <summary>
	''' The EditLinks PortalModuleBase is used to manage the Links
	''' </summary>
    ''' <remarks>
	''' </remarks>
	''' <history>
	''' 	[cnurse]	9/23/2004	Moved Links to a separate Project
